# Phase 1 Autonomous Completion Rule

When the user asks to **complete Phase 1**, **finish Phase 1 without involvement**, or run full Phase 1 validation end-to-end:

1. Read [`ai-agents/phase-1/phase-1-autonomous-completion-agent.md`](ai-agents/phase-1/phase-1-autonomous-completion-agent.md)
2. Use skill [`.cursor/skills/stream-heaven/phase-1/phase-1-autonomous-completion-agent/basic/SKILL.md`](.cursor/skills/stream-heaven/phase-1/phase-1-autonomous-completion-agent/basic/SKILL.md) for `pnpm run phase1:complete`
3. Use [advanced skill](.cursor/skills/stream-heaven/phase-1/phase-1-autonomous-completion-agent/advanced/SKILL.md) for fix loops, docs, and gap closure
4. Delegate tooling regressions to [`phase-1-remediation-agent.md`](ai-agents/phase-1/phase-1-remediation-agent.md)

Run `pnpm run phase1:complete` before handoff. Do not regenerate agents with `generate-agents.mjs`.
